name: FloatingWindowSize

properties.name: ONE_FIFTH
properties.description: The floating window is one fifth the length and height of the movie's original display size.

properties.name: ONE_FOURTH
properties.description: The floating window is one fourth the length and height of the movie's original display size.

properties.name: ONE_HALF
properties.description: The floating window is one half the length and height of the movie's original display size.

properties.name: FULL
properties.description: The floating window is the movie's original display size.

properties.name: TWICE
properties.description: The floating window is twice the length and height of the movie's original display size.

properties.name: TRIPLE
properties.description: The floating window is triple the length and height of the movie's original display size.

properties.name: QUADRUPLE
properties.description: The floating window is quadruple the length and height of the movie's original display size.

properties.name: MAX
properties.description: The floating window fills the entire screen.

description: The size of the movie's floating window. Valid only when floating window is true.
